Hi @Andrew Wingate,
@stuart mentioned that he would need wire bonding diagrams for each project to reduce the chance of bonding a chip the wrong way around, for example. Since some of the chips have distinctive features, I could provide you with a rendering of the top metal layer for each project, which you could then combine with a screenshot of the PCB and add the bond wire connections.

Would it be fine if I provide you the images with their ID as names, so that you can automate the bonding diagram creation?
